CompileFlags:
    Add: [--std=c++20, -Ilibs/boost_1_81_0/boost/]
    Compiler: clang++-15

Diagnostics:
    ClangTidy:
        Add: [bugprone*, performance*, readability*, modernize*]
        Remove: [readability-identifier-length, readability-magic-numbers, modernize-avoid-c-arrays]
        IndentWidth: 4

